episodes.title: 89. 8 Passengers - Kevin Can Wait (Ruby Franke, Jodi Hildebrandt & ConneXions, Part 11)
episodes.description: We’re rolling the tapes back now. We’ve been building up anticipation about Kevin Franke’s interview with the police, and we promise it won’t disappoint. Kevin’s testimony is important for a number of different ways, most notably for the things he says and the way he says them. You’ll hear Kevin touch on all different topics like how Ruby and Jodi first met, how he was swindled into ConneXions via Jodi’s famous Men’s Group offerings, and what made Jodi such a compelling personality when it came to getting folks on board in a cult. You’ll hear Kevin’s zombie-like delivery and you might even hear him snap out of it for a bit… only to retreat back into the darkness again.
